name: Marshall PEDL-00045 JVM 4 Way Footswitch
details:
4 Way Switch designed for use with the Marshall JVM Series of Heads and CombosMarshall JVM 4 Way Foot Controller is a four way programmable footswitch with Memory. Authorized Marshall controller for the JVM Series. Blank areas above switches can be tailored to your preferences. These use a simple 1/4" plug. Can work with other Marshall series but check first.
